Wings beating, Tyrael lands on a short but strong tree, almost devoid 
of leaves, on the island Cignar had chosen. He had wondered who was 
the other guest the Predacon had talked about and figured out it could 
be only the Rogues or the Maximals. He was not certain who he would 
prefer to see...

--- In nbwrpg@y..., Rudra656@a... wrote:
> ::Cygnar::
>        He glances at his handy chronometer.  "It's time for my 
meeting.  He 
> walks out past Cryotek.  "Soon, we will attack.  Until I return you 
are in 
> charge."  He leaves the base and takes off into he air, heading for 
the 
> island.
